  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended to predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors. Seven factors are assessed; six are flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. All assessed factors show achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels under this Minimal-profile submission. Decision: Accepted for the stated VAD use scope as described in the bound Claim and Requirement records.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-prediction-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-experimental-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-hemolysis-benchmark-dataset"
  ],
